ogin-state mutation through the view model.\",\n74:         \"LoginScreen performs screen-entry setup by creating scaffold state, wiring a `LaunchedEffect(key1 = true)` collector for one-shot UI events, and applying status/navigation bar colors while the login screen is active.\",\n75:         \"Successful login triggers persisted session-state mutation through `LoginViewModel` and `LoginRepository.toggleLoginState()`, so the screen changes a stored login preference rather than only local UI state.\"\n76:       ],\n77:       \"acceptanceEvidence\": [\n78:         \"Closed critical/high features must record sourceBehavior, targetBehavior, parityLevel, targetEndpoints, and verificationEvidence.\",\n79:         \"Build pass alone is not per-feature verification.\",\n80:         \"Referenced target tests are not strong evidence until a latest test gate PASS or explicit harness blocker is recorded.\"\n81:       ],\n82:       \"riskHints\": [\n83:         \"critical/high behavior cannot close on build pass alone\"\n84:       ],\n85:       \"matrixRows\": [\n86:         {\n87:           \"kind\": \"source-feature\",\n88:           \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-login-b030a7b1f9-001-image-viewing-bitmap-exif-handling-zoom\",\n89:           \"featureName\": \"Image viewing, bitmap/exif handling, zoom, preview, or gallery display behavior.\",\n90:           \"sourcePath\": \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/login/LoginScreen.kt\",\n91:           \"importance\": \"critical\",\n92:           \"plannedPhase\": \"phase-03-onboarding-login-profile\",\n93:           \"status\": \"not-applicable\",\n94:           \"parityLevel\": \"not-applicable\",\n95:           \"verdict\": \"complete\",\n96:           \"reasons\": [\n97:             \"not-applicable has source/notes explanation\"\n98:           ],\n99:           \"targetEndpoints\": [\n100:             \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/login/login_page