tInput` components, clears stale errors when fields change, and re-renders immediately on invalid-login updates while keeping one-shot feedback through toast emission.\",\n921:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\n922:         \"Source review: D:/Kotlin2Cangjie/Foodike/app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/login/LoginScreen.kt reads `val email by viewModel.email`, `val password by viewModel.password`, and collects `eventFlow` inside `LaunchedEffect` to show snackbar feedback.\",\n923:         \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj declares `@State` loginEmail, loginPassword, and loginErrorMessage, updates them from `renderLoginRoute`, and reuses them in `performLogin` and `clearLoginError`.\",\n924:         \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/login/login_page.cj::renderLoginRoute binds the observed values into text inputs and the error banner so field edits and invalid-login state changes propagate immediately in the visible UI.\",\n925:         \"Test verification: `C:/Users/Sieger/.cangjie-sdk/6.1/cangjie/build-tools/tools/bin/cjpm.exe test --target aarch64-linux-ohos` passed in `D:/workspace/Foodike/Foodike-Harmony/entry`, including `phase03_onboarding_login_profile_test.cj::Phase03OnboardingLoginProfileTest.loginStoreAcceptsOnlySourceCredentials`.\"\n926:       ],\n927:       \"parityLevel\": \"equivalent\",\n928:       \"targetEndpoints\": [\n929:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.loginEmail\",\n930:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.loginPassword\",\n931:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.loginErrorMessage\",\n932:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.clearLoginError\",\n933:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_ent