es the shell-owned cart command and home/history tab commands, and limits shell chrome to the same home/history-at-top contract as `SetupNavigation` in the source app.\",\n3509:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\n3510:         \"Manual code review: entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onCreate resolves `bootstrapStartRoute` before entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onWindowStageCreate loads the bootstrap page, preserving the source startup-owned shell handoff.\",\n3511:         \"Manual code review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute, showBottomShell, and runPrimaryAction now compose route-specific surfaces and shell commands instead of a route picker/debug dashboard.\",\n3512:         \"Test verification: `cjpm.exe test --target aarch64-linux-ohos` passed in `D:\\\\workspace\\\\Foodike\\\\Foodike-Harmony\\\\entry` with the phase test env overlay on 2026-06-25, covering entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj including `primaryActionTargetsMatchShellContract`, `bottomShellOnlyShowsOnTopLevelHomeAndHistoryRoutes`, `resolvesLoggedOutUsersToOnboarding`, and `resolvesLoggedInUsersToHome`.\"\n3513:       ],\n3514:       \"parityLevel\": \"equivalent\",\n3515:       \"targetEndpoints\": [\n3516:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onCreate\",\n3517:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::bootstrapStartRoute\",\n3518:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute\",\n3519:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.showBottomShell\",\n3520:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.runPrimaryAction\",\n3521:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj::primaryActionTarget\"\n3522:       ],\n3523:       \"tests\": [\n3524:        